  04 Jun 2015; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org>
  kchmviewer-6.0-r1.ebuild, kchmviewer-6.1.ebuild, kchmviewer-7.1.ebuild:
  Move various kde-base packages to kde-apps.

  31 Oct 2014; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> kchmviewer-7.1.ebuild:
  Solve parallel build failure wrt bug #527192.

  17 Oct 2014; Michael Palimaka <kensington@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add upstream metadata.

